publisher			Strategy First							
publish_time	 2008年9月18日		
desc_long								关于这款游戏							Race 18 of Ford and Land Rover’s toughest off road trucks, 4X4’s and SUV’s through lush environments, stunning scenery and extreme terrain.Choose from 12 distinct race types as you jump, bump and power slide powerful off road vehicles across 24 sweeping tracks designed for high-speed racing. Find the alternative routes to gain an advantage in your bid to be first past the finish line. With acceleration faster than any previous Ford game, real time, on-the-go vehicle damage repair and ingame pick-ups, Off Road is an adrenalin-pumping, high-speed racing experience.• 18 officially licensed Ford and Land Rover offroad vehicles. (Including concept vehiclesnot seen in any other game).• 12 distinct race types.• 24 detailed tracks.• 3 beautifully detailed off road environments.• Real time, on-the-go damage repair.• Pick up and play handling.• Discover hidden routes.• Power sliding - throw powerful trucksaround the tracks.• In-game pickups: Discover repair pods, timeextensions, artifacts and cash.• Multi-player racing via split screen.						
